description:
M-Net kicks off its local offering with a celebrity version of the popular cooking series, but with a twist. All celebrities taking part in the show are playing to win money for a charity of their choice!




Celebrity MasterChef South Africa - Season 1, Episode 1



In the first episode of Celebrity MasterChef, the judges challenged the contestants to travel back to their childhood with cherished and time-honoured dishes that invoked their memories of long ago. Some of these dishes may have reminded you of your own childhood, while others are sure to give you the inspiration to try something new.



Original Air Date: 08-Feb-2015
